  "detailed_description": "The setting in the game is relatively simple, this is the last test to become the Interstellar Authority, you can use more weapons than ever before, such as shotguns, two-handed guns, explosive grenades, etc., to go to the target planet to take down powerful enemies. The battle scene is three-layered, for example, standing on the second layer can hit the first layer, but not the other way around. In short, it will be a crazy battle, see the interstellar badge, it is waiting for you to light up in the light boat.",
  "about_the_game": "The setting in the game is relatively simple, this is the last test to become the Interstellar Authority, you can use more weapons than ever before, such as shotguns, two-handed guns, explosive grenades, etc., to go to the target planet to take down powerful enemies. The battle scene is three-layered, for example, standing on the second layer can hit the first layer, but not the other way around. In short, it will be a crazy battle, see the interstellar badge, it is waiting for you to light up in the light boat.",
